:0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:07:40.000Z","msg":"同佢個仔排定公屋未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e0b9edea7de915ea6a214ce732aafbe6d67721","tid":447450,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"無人識你咁撚慘呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫下你手<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong>我唔係屈機男 #40470</strong> 簡介:<br />\n<br />\n於高登經常扮有錢佬教化眾高登仔做人道理, 被會員 米已成炊 質疑其有錢背景, 及後屈機男發明捐錢比賽及第一次敗走退出高登 (但事後依然有鬼鼠上高登)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114008_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114008_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg&h=ae37653c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114421_6bd8407bf6d5ceee8602e3fad4c3511f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114421_6bd8407bf6d5ceee8602e3fad4c3511f.jpg&h=7048e721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/113834_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F113834_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg&h=0192c6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/113811_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F113811_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg&h=ac60eca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男 敗走後在連登重新插旗, 廣納信徒, 繼續以有錢佬姿態教化蒼生...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114136_20d860a4ad7eeb3a978fe80fdf4162f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114136_20d860a4ad7eeb3a978fe80fdf4162f7.jpg&h=b2af6d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員 米已成炊 狙擊趕至, <strong>我唔係屈機男</strong> 發起第2次鬥捐錢活動, 並再次以<strong>敗者永久退出連登</strong>為賭注<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/216195/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/216195/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114554_d63c6683aa8e5ec7011afc9beb8e082e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114554_d63c6683aa8e5ec7011afc9beb8e082e.jpg&h=56996aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次結果更加柒, 自己開盤自己潛水, 會員 米已成炊 不戰而勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/217870/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/217870/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114851_dd793b0a7bdc7b6717320a1b5602eb1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114851_dd793b0a7bdc7b6717320a1b5602eb1a.jpg&h=0c512bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日走數狗 <strong>我唔係屈機男 #40470</strong> 言而無信又再一次上水...</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f35dd87ffde2e6b402e7b00918f7e85cb9949637","tid":447450,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}